    <div class="container w-60 border-style">
      <h3 class="my-3 font-weight-bold">Results</h3>
      <div class="container px-0">
        <p>The ability to donate a dollar to the cause of your choice while completing regular Venmo transactions
           was integrated to the existing app. The social aspect, that makes Venmo unique and distinctive, is enhanced
            by showing donations made by others in the user feed. User got the feeling of being secure dealing with charity
            as he is the one who makes a choice of the organization to support and decide whether or not it needs to be public.</p>
      </div>
