          <h3 class="text-center my-5">Key takeaways from interviews:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Everyone wants the donation process to be <b>quick and easy.</b></li>
            <li>Users are more likely to donate when they are <b>offered to do so.</b></li>
            <li>Venmo is mostly used for <b>small amount transactions</b>, often to split the charge among a group of people.</li>
            <li>When you donate it is important to know <b>where your money is going.</b></li>
            <li>People enjoy friends and family</li>
            <li><b>Anonymity</b> should always be an option</li>
          </ul>
